items.title: Western Wealth Capital sells Tempe apartments for $25.7 million
items.summary:
Cushman & Wakefield completed the sale of Anzio Apartment Homes, located at 1330 West Broadway Road in Tempe, Arizona. An entity formed by Laguna Point Properties, LLC of Laguna Hills, California purchased the property from WWC VII, LLC, a company formed by Western Wealth Capital of North Vancouver, British Columbia, for $25.7 million. David Fogler and Steven Nicoluzakis of Cushman & Wakefield represented the seller. Anzio Apartment Homes is a 240-unit, Class B garden-style apartment!

The post Western Wealth Capital sells Tempe apartments for $25.7 million appeared first on AZ Big Media.
